IF UPDATE_INDICATOR EQ 'I'.

  IF DATA_IMRG-AMOSTRA IS NOT INITIAL .
    MOVE DATA_IMRG-AMOSTRA TO AMOSTRA.
  ENDIF.

ELSEIF UPDATE_INDICATOR EQ 'U'.

  IF DATA_IMRG_OLD-AMOSTRA IS NOT INITIAL.
    IF DATA_IMRG_OLD-AMOSTRA NE DATA_IMRG-AMOSTRA.
      MOVE DATA_IMRG-AMOSTRA TO AMOSTRA.
    ELSE.
      MOVE DATA_IMRG_OLD-AMOSTRA TO AMOSTRA.
    ENDIF.
  ENDIF.

ENDIF.

CALL SCREEN 0100 STARTING AT 15 5.

MOVE: AMOSTRA TO UPDATE_DATA_IMRG-AMOSTRA.
MOVE: DATA_IMRG-MDOCM TO UPDATE_DATA_IMRG-MDOCM.
CLEAR: WA_IMRG, AMOSTRA.
